title: nTrackStudioEX 8 0 0 3380
description:
- Block in firewall - install the app.
- Copy and replace cracked files in default dir.
- Open program. Click on "Activation" in Help tab while pressing "Shift" button on your keyboard to get the offline activation screen. Make sure you're holding shift button on your keyboard when pressing activation. Or see manual 1.3.2 for details.
- Copy your machine ID to keygen and generate your reg code. Register with it.
- Restart the app to take effects
